               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17890114-24-person284">
                  JOSEPH
                   WALKER
               <interp inst="t17890114-24-person284" type="surname" value="WALKER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890114-24-person284" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890114-24-person284" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , GUILTY, Death.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice BULLER.</p>
